This seems like a bug in the ide driver not issuing a reset?
On RH7.3 (2.4.18-3) if I do:
$ hdparm -Y /dev/hda
$ do stuff and disk spins up
$ hdparm -Y /dev/hda
$ everything hangs waiting for disk
